Superb drone flight by @hunterkowald 🤯 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on tripfever.net (link in my bio: @tripfever)

📽 @hunterkowald
📍 Los Angeles, California
🎶 Highway to Hell - AC/DC
